{"id":"2791866672","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2791866672","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjc5MTg2NjY3Mg==","status":"current","title":"Análisis de operación get_products - commerce-suite","version":{"by":{"type":"known","accountId":"5f3d2a10ea5e2f003979db69","accountType":"atlassian","email":"","publicName":"Ignacio Jorge","profilePicture":{"path":"/wiki/aa-avatar/5f3d2a10ea5e2f003979db69","width":48,"height":48,"isDefault":false},"displayName":"Ignacio Jorge","isExternalCollaborator":false,"isGuest":false,"locale":"en_US","accountStatus":"active","_expandable":{"operations":"","personalSpace":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/user?accountId=5f3d2a10ea5e2f003979db69"}},"when":"2023-12-01T16:58:27.992Z","friendlyWhen":"Dec 01, 2023","message":"","number":1,"minorEdit":false,"ncsStepVersion":"2854","ncsStepVersionSource":"ncs-ack","confRev":"confluence$content$2791866672.72","contentTypeModified":false,"_expandable":{"collaborators":"","content":"/rest/api/content/2791866672"},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2791866672/version/1"}},"ancestors":[{"id":"2178416778","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2178416778","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjE3ODQxNjc3OA==","status":"current","title":"Bancard","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":878},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2316959745","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2316959745","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjMxNjk1OTc0NQ==","status":"current","title":"TMP","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":887957284},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2316959745","tinyui":"/x/AQAaig","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2316959745","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2316959745/TMP","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2316959745"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p>Este documento se centra en abordar un problema de rendimiento identificado en una operaci&oacute;n espec&iacute;fica del portal de comercios. A trav&eacute;s de este an&aacute;lisis, buscamos identificar las causas subyacentes, evaluar el impacto y proponer soluciones para mejorar la velocidad y la estabilidad de la operaci&oacute;n.</p><h2>Informaci&oacute;n General</h2><p>Plataforma: Infonet Cobranzas<br />Proyecto: commerce-suite<br />Operaci&oacute;n: <a href=\"https://koj45011.live.dynatrace.com/#smgd;sci=SERVICE-9164FE6A7CFFB283;tab=RT;servicefilter=0%1E10%11SERVICE_METHOD_GROUP-40FD84C8433AADD6%109%11SERVICE_METHOD-AB00624499E567ED%14http:%5C0%5C0127.0.0.1:8083%5C0services%5C0epos%5C0cashiers%5C0get_products;gtf=-1h;gf=all;timeframe=custom1701201450000to1701201750000\"><u>/services/epos/cashiers/get_products</u></a></p><h2>Motivaci&oacute;n</h2><p>Este an&aacute;lisis se encuentra motivado por las siguiente consideraciones:</p><ul><li><p>Infonet cobranzas es una plataforma que cuenta al d&iacute;a de hoy con mucho potencial de mejoras en cuanto a performance y en la que se quiere poner especial &eacute;nfasis de cara al 2024.</p></li><li><p>La operaci&oacute;n a analizar, resulta ser la operaci&oacute;n con el tiempo medio de respuesta mas alto de commerce-suite, registrando un tiempo medio total de 4.89 segundos, y de 8.8 segundos en el 5% mas lento. Un tiempo de respuesta que afecta considerablemente la experiencia de usuario.<br /></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"293\" ac:original-width=\"1795\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:width=\"736\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20231128-203949.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image></li><li><p>Esta operaci&oacute;n es una de las 10 operaciones mas consumidas de commerce-suite con un total de 12,8 solicitudes/minuto. A su vez, es la operaci&oacute;n que mas tiempo de ejecuci&oacute;n consume de commerce-suite.<br /></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"103\" ac:original-width=\"446\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:width=\"446\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20231128-204032.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"246\" ac:original-width=\"1801\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:width=\"736\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20231128-204204.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image></li></ul><p>Para extraer todas estas mediciones y evidencias se utiliz&oacute; un timeframe de 1 semana.</p><h2>Investigaci&oacute;n</h2><p>La operaci&oacute;n con problemas tiene dos consultas a servicios externos</p><ul><li><p><code>get_commerce_branch_products</code> en epos-service<br /></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"186\" ac:original-width=\"1811\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:width=\"736\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20231130-143357.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p>59.8ms tiempo medio de respuesta<br />86.6ms tiempo medio del 5% mas lento</p></li><li><p><code>get_products_report</code> en billing-service<br /></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"191\" ac:original-width=\"1816\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:width=\"736\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20231130-144642.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p>37.5ms tiempo medio de respuesta<br />49.1ms tiempo medio del 5% mas lento</p></li></ul><p>Con esta informaci&oacute;n y teniendo en cuenta que ademas ambas operaciones se cachean usando dory, se puede deducir que los problemas de performance no son a causa de las consultas a los servicios externos a commerce-suite, sino que se encuentra en el mismo portal.</p>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2791866672"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":791366735},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2791866672/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2791866672/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2791866672/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2791866672/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2791866672","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2791866672/An+lisis+de+operaci+n+get_products+-+commerce-suite","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2791866672","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2791866672","tinyui":"/x/MIFopg","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}